text: Carron Mountain () is a mountain 440m high on the border of County Limerick and County Cork, Ireland. It is part of the Ballyhoura Mountains. Carron is home to the North Cork transmitter for the UPC MMDS service. ==References== == External links == * Listing at mountainviews.ie Category:Mountains and hills of County Limerick Category:Mountains and hills of County Cork
title: Carron Mountain
